vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting the renewal of Specific Use Permit No. 2278 for an extended-hours historic house museum and meeting space and fundraising use on property zoned Area G within Planned Development District No. 63, on the southeast corner of Swiss Avenue and Parkmont Street
Recommendation of Staff and CPC:  Approval for a period expiring on January 24, 2024, subject to conditions
Z190-323(CT)
